title: Impressive Remodel, Heat Paid, Walk to Dining & Shopping, Dog Park!
posting_body: ['Contact info:', 'Mike Miller | The Apartment Resource |', 'show contact info', '1BR/1Ba - Walk to Shopping/Dining, Private Balcony & Community Sauna!', 'Hwy 61, Maplewood, MN', '$1395/mo', 'KEY FEATURES', 'Sq Footage:', '800 sqft.', 'Bedroom:', '1', 'Bathroom:', '1', 'Parking:', '2 Dedicated', 'Lease Duration:', '12 Months', 'Deposit:', '$500', 'Pets Policy:', 'Cats & Dogs OK', 'Laundry:', 'Laundry Facilities on Property', 'Property Type:', 'Apartment', 'DESCRIPTION', 'We are a short walk to shopping and dinning at Maplewood Mall and Osaka Sushi and Hibachi.', 'With amazing garden waterfalls and a dog park for your four legged friends, this breathtaking community features a gorgeous tree-filled courtyard and offers a picnic area with barbecue grills which is perfect for entertaining your guests.', 'We offer 1Br and 2Br apartments for rent with balconies, or porches, some with split-bedroom floor plans, perfect for roommates.', 'Your dog will love the specially designed pet park to run wild, and your cat will enjoy the panoramic views outside your home!', 'Exquisite interiors, an fully equipped community room, heated underground parking, fitness room and a sauna are just a few of the amenities you will find here.', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Prices and availability are subject to change.', 'Photos may not represent exact unit.', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', 'Heat, Water, and Trash Included', 'Controlled Building Access', 'Heated Underground Parking', 'Close to Shopping, Restaurants and Downtown', 'Car wash', 'Bicycle Racks', 'Elevator in Building', '24-Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Balcony/Patio on All Homes', 'High Speed Internet Available', 'Fitness Center', 'Laundry facilities on property', 'Community Room', 'Pets Welcome!', 'Contact info:', 'Mike Miller', 'The Apartment Resource', 'show contact info']
